                "invention-title": [
                    "Thermal power generating unit zero-carbon transformation method based on combined energy storage and flexible electricity abandoning hydrogen production",
                    "基于联合储能与灵活性弃电制氢的火电机组零碳改造方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a thermal power generating unit zero-carbon transformation method based on combined energy storage and flexible electricity abandoning hydrogen production. The thermal power generating unit zero-carbon transformation method comprises the following steps that 1, a system structure of a coal-fired thermal power generating unit zero-carbon transformation method based on 100% renewable energy, fused salt heat storage-storage battery combined energy storage and flexible electricity abandoning hydrogen production is constructed; 2, a combined power generation system operation strategy based on coal-fired thermal power unit transformation is formulated; 3, based on the system structures and the operation strategies in the step 1 and the step 2, establishing a capacity configuration optimization model of the coal-fired thermal power generating unit flexibility transformation method; and 4, solving the capacity configuration optimization model by using a teaching heuristic optimization algorithm TLBO. The method is suitable for the technical field of thermal power generating unit transformation, realizes zero-carbon transformation of the thermal power generating unit, reduces the consumption of coal resources, relieves the problem of coal resource deficiency, realizes sustainable and low-carbon transformation of a power system, and improves the power generation efficiency. And the stability of continuous operation of the thermal power generating unit is ensured."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了基于联合储能与灵活性弃电制氢的火电机组零碳改造方法，包括以下步骤：步骤1：构建基于100％可再生能源、熔盐储热‑蓄电池联合储能、以及灵活性弃电制氢的燃煤火电机组零碳改造方法的系统结构；步骤2：制定基于燃煤火电机组改造的联合发电系统运行策略；步骤3：基于步骤1及步骤2所述的系统结构及运行策略，建立燃煤火电机组灵活性改造方法的容量配置优化模型；步骤4：利用教学启发式优化算法TLBO对容量配置优化模型进行求解，本发明适用于火电机组改造技术领域，实现了火电机组零碳改造，降低了煤炭资源的消耗，缓解了煤炭资源匮乏问题，实现了电力系统的可持续性及低碳化转型，确保了火电机组持续运行的稳定性。"
                }
            ]
